## Combat Adaptations

### 1. PvP-Specific Abilities
Some abilities work differently:
```
PvE: Stun lasts 3 turns
PvP: Stun lasts 1 turn

PvE: Heal restores 50% HP
PvP: Heal restores 25% HP

PvE: Ultimate has 5 turn cooldown
PvP: Ultimate has 8 turn cooldown
```

### 2. Crowd Control Diminishing Returns
- First stun: 100% duration
- Second stun: 50% duration
- Third stun: 25% duration
- Immunity for 2 turns after

### 3. Turn Timers
- 60 seconds per turn
- 15 second warning
- Auto-play basic action if timeout
- Forfeit after 3 timeouts

